00:20:01.360 --> 00:20:04.660
And often those were
very sad sales, actually,

00:20:04.660 --> 00:20:06.310
back during the Depression.

00:20:06.310 --> 00:20:10.280
Also, he claimed that Charlie
Higgins knew a thousand tunes,

00:20:10.280 --> 00:20:13.510
