00:22:23.590 --> 00:22:27.830
and that's, again, the
work that became the bible

00:22:27.830 --> 00:22:31.760
for revivalists in
the '50s and '60s.

00:22:31.760 --> 00:22:34.480
Alan was working on his video.

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:37.730
This was one of his last
major projects, well,

00:22:37.730 --> 00:22:39.690
