00:25:39.480 --> 00:25:43.320
Okay. So that was a short story

00:25:43.320 --> 00:25:45.410
about the Lomaxes and
their collecting.

00:25:45.410 --> 00:25:49.760
And then my main topic is the
roots of the banjo and the fiddle.

00:25:49.760 --> 00:25:53.300
The banjo's heard around the world
from the Blue Ridge Mountains

00:25:53.300 --> 00:25:58.510
to the American Folklife
Center, to Switzerland and Japan.

00:25:58.510 --> 00:26:05.210
And the White Mountain musician has
been the symbol of that instrument.

00:26:05.210 --> 00:26:10.240
And this recording of the
