00:26:27.800 --> 00:26:32.950
I'll tell you a little
story about Doc Watson.

00:26:32.950 --> 00:26:39.100
When Ralph Winslow from
the Smithsonian met him,

00:26:39.100 --> 00:26:43.900
Doc was playing electric guitar

00:26:43.900 --> 00:26:48.900
and so he Ralph was only
interested in recording Tom Ashley.

00:26:48.900 --> 00:26:55.130
But then, one of these days in
