00:30:08.230 --> 00:30:11.040
These are the guys sitting out
in the woods with their jug

00:30:11.040 --> 00:30:17.630
of liquor telling stories and
listening to their dogs rove.

00:30:17.630 --> 00:30:22.240
And in Dink's version of "Fox
Chase" he says at the end,

00:30:22.240 --> 00:30:26.680 position:56%
God bless my red eyes, the fox says,
