00:53:15.310 --> 00:53:18.770
And notice some of these moves.

00:53:18.770 --> 00:53:23.090
Those are the Laurent banjo
players, like heaving down.

00:53:23.090 --> 00:53:28.420
&gt;&gt; From me and do you want
